About
==================
StarPlanner is a Starcraft: Brood Wars bot that uses Goal-Oriented Action Planning for it's decision making mechanism. It was created as part of the dissertation project of Panagiotis Peikidis title "StarPlanner: Demonstrating the use of planning in a video game"

Links
==================
StarPlanner site: http://pekalicious.com/starplanner
Goal-Oritented Action Planning: http://web.media.mit.edu/~jorkin/goap.html